# Product Controls Module — FROZEN

**Frozen:** 2026-06-21 (category-module-freeze branch)

The Product Controls module is approved for freeze. Do not modify Product Controls-related code without explicit user approval.

## Scope

### Product Controls
- Reusable single-line business controls (`CTL-` numbering)
- Fields: control number, name, control type, status
- Modal CRUD, archive/restore (super_admin only)
- No descriptions, SEO, AI, or content management

### Control Groups
- Policy bundles (`CTG-` numbering)
- Fields: group number, name, assigned controls (min 1 active), controls_count, status
- Controls | Groups tabs on existing Product Catalog → Controls page only

## Official control types (7)

1. Warranty
2. Guarantee
3. Return Policy
4. Replacement Policy
5. Handling Alert
6. Usage Note
7. Warning

Do not add control types without explicit approval. Specific business rules belong in the control name text.

## Data policy

- **No standard controls seeder** — business lines are created manually
- Control groups are built from manually created controls
- Immutable numbers: `control_number`, `group_number`

## Permissions

| Action | Staff | Super Admin |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| View / Create / Edit | Yes | Yes |
| Archive / Restore | No | Yes |

## Future products integration (deferred)

Products will later support individual controls, control groups, or both. Do not implement product pivots without explicit approval.

## Config keys (frozen)

`config/product-catalog.php`: `control_statuses`, `control_group_statuses`, `control_types`
